## Limitations

The analysis is based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible trends affecting companies. Additionally, the interpretation of trends is subject to the context provided by the sources, which may not fully capture the nuances of specific industries or regions. Future research could benefit from more industry-specific data and case studies to provide a more tailored analysis.

